    The code returns the following error:

    br is a void element tag and must neither have `children` nor use `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`.

    Version 2
    Deployed
    Edited

    I've provided a general fix approach since the specific line causing the error isn't visible in the code snippets you shared. The error occurs when a <br> tag is used incorrectly with either:

    1. Content between opening and closing tags (<br>content</br>)
    2. Using the dangerouslySetInnerHTML prop on a <br> tag

    The correct usage is always a self-closing tag: <br /> with no children or content.

    If you can share the specific line where the error occurs, I can provide a more targeted fix.
